| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2408 — Recovery Inhibition (thegentlemen)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 97bfc262-36ae-5c0b-9d91-3093d092c660"
